{
  "stem": "14613.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's the way we came here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were both Jews and Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And first, we came to New York.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in New York, they separated the different religious boys and girls, depending on their religious denomination.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they sent them out to-- the Catholics to the Catholic auspices, the Jews on the Jewish auspices, and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So since we did not have anybody, my brother and myself were sent to Atlanta, Georgia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived-- we lived with a Jewish family that, as I said, the US government sent-- they dispersed the people to different cities and gave the jurisdiction to different organizations, so that our organization in Atlanta was, I believe, a Hebrew orphans home.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they placed us with a family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a Jewish family that lived in Atlanta.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember, although I'm trying to forget it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we did not have a very pleasant experience with this family, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a family which was very well off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took us there, to their home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they really did not understand, or maybe they did not want to understand the problems with the survivors.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they did not understand that when they take us to their home, and that when we go to school, we need to have breakfast.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We need to have lunch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had no money to buy breakfast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had no money to buy lunch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And since we did not get this there-- because maybe they took it as natural that we can buy and do whatever we want-- we would go to school with no breakfast and no lunch.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I know after a few months, we wanted to go back to Europe.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
